Title: An Act Changing the Name of Sulu Pilot Opportunity School of Fisheries in the Municipality of Bongao, Province of Tawi-Tawi, to Tawi-Tawi Pilot Opportunity School of Fisheries
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 207
An Act Changing the Name of Sulu Pilot Opportunity School of Fisheries in the Municipality of Bongao, Province of Tawi-Tawi, to Tawi-Tawi Pilot Opportunity School of Fisheries
Section 1. The name of Sulu Pilot Opportunity School of Fisheries, located at Sanga-Sanga in the Municipality of Bongao, Province of Tawi-Tawi, is hereby changed to Tawi-Tawi Pilot Opportunity School of Fisheries.
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.1Ã¢wphi1
Approved: March 25, 1982
